  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing the Border**\n\nI\'m currently focused on designing the `DrawingBorder.tsx` component. The aim is to create background decorations mimicking the hand-drawn style of the landing page. My initial design incorporates cute outline drawings including faces, trees, notebook doodles, a computer, a book, a lightbulb, pencils, and hearts.\n\n\n**Expanding the Decoration**\n\nI\'m now thinking about hand-drawn marker-style arrows in various colors (blue, pink, orange, green, yellow). I plan to use clean vector SVG paths to create these drawings and scatter them responsively around the page, achieving that playful yet high-fidelity look, adapting to different screen sizes. I\'m also planning a responsive component to beautifully arrange the decorative illustrations around the central card content. I\'ve also added some items to draw: kid\'s face, book, cloud, pencil, tree, lightbulb, windmill, and globe.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 21
      nanos: 954577031
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
