  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Appreciating the Design**\n\nI find the design remarkably beautiful. The use of Lucide-react icons, alongside clean shapes, achieves a mature aesthetic appropriate for the target age group. The focus is on a design that avoids childish elements while maintaining appeal. This provides a compelling combination of functionality and aesthetic value.\n\n\n**Building the Activities**\n\nI\'m focused on creating the functional components now, especially the workspace elements. I\'m building out a comprehensive `ClassroomDashboard` alongside modular topic activities as a way to allow real testing. I will add in these specific modules: `FrancaisActivity`, `MathsActivity`, and `EveilActivity` as the core. I want the activities to be fully functional within the dashboard itself.\n\n\n"
